Tater, I'm not touching <abbr title="Realism Overhaul (mod)">RO</abbr> with a 10ft pole, too complex. I made a simple patch to balance <abbr title="Specific Impulse (rocketry) or Internet Service Provider">ISP</abbr>/thrust for a bare <abbr title="Real Solar System (mod)">RSS</abbr> install, no need to go further for me personally.

Spoiler

@PART[\*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleEngines\*]]:NEEDS[RealSolarSystem]:AFTER[SSTU]  

{  

    @MODULE[ModuleEngines\*]  

    {  

        @maxThrust \*= 2.0

        @atmosphereCurve  

        {  

            @key[1, ] \*= 1.6  

            @key,1[1, ] \*= 1.6  

            @key,2[1, ] \*= 1.6  

        }  

    }  

}

// optional  

@PART[\*]:HAS[@MODULE[SSTUModularHeatShield]]:NEEDS[RealSolarSystem]  

{  

    @RESOURCE[Ablator]  

    {  

        @amount \*= 2.5  

        @maxAmoun \*= 2.5  

    }  

}

